data.description: 3BR 1 Bath apartment upstairs. 2BR 1 Bath apartment downstairs in very nice quiet neighborhood. Bustleton section of Northeast Philly.  Large bedrooms, a lot of closet space, ceiling fans in each bedroom, fenced in yard, wood floors throughout. Brand new floors in master bedroom, new kitchen tile, brand new central air and energy efficient heating system, brand new windows.   Appliances Included:  Washer  Dryer Refrigerator    Kitchen, D/W upstairs, hot water heater, toilet, and faucets, central air unit all new.   3 off street parking spaces and fenced in yard.
